Package: libntl44-shlibs
Version: 11.5.1
Revision: 1
GCC: 4.0
Maintainer: None <fink-devel@lists.sourceforge.net>
Description: Library for doing number theory
Source: https://www.shoup.net/ntl/ntl-%v.tar.gz
Source-Checksum: SHA256(210d06c31306cbc6eaf6814453c56c776d9d8e8df36d74eb306f6a523d1c6a8a)
SourceDirectory: ntl-%v/src
BuildDepends: <<
	fink-package-precedence,
	gmp5 (>= 6.2.1-1),
	libtool2
<<
Depends: <<
	gmp5-shlibs (>= 6.2.1-1)
<<
PatchScript: <<
	perl -pi -e 's/(-version-info)/-no-undefined \1/' mfile
<<
CompileScript: <<
	./configure DEF_PREFIX=%p SHARED=on LIBTOOL=glibtool CPPFLAGS=-MD NTL_NO_INIT_TRANS=on
	make
	fink-package-precedence --prohibit-bdep=libntl44 --depfile-ext='\.d' .
<<
InfoTest: <<
	TestScript: <<
		make check || exit 2
		fink-package-precedence --prohibit-bdep=libntl44 --depfile-ext='\.d' .
	<<
<<
InstallScript:<<
	make install PREFIX=%i DOCDIR=%i/share/doc/libntl44
	rm %i/lib/libntl.a
<<
DocFiles: ../README ../doc/copying.txt:LICENSE
Shlibs: %p/lib/libntl.44.dylib 45.0.0 %n (>= 11.5.1-1)
SplitOff: <<
	Package: libntl44
	Depends: %N (= %v-%r)
	Conflicts: ntl, ntl-64bit, libntl29, libntl30, libntl39, libntl44
	Replaces: ntl, ntl-64bit, libntl29, libntl30, libntl39, libntl44
	BuildDependsOnly: true
	Files: <<
		include
		lib/libntl.{dylib,la}
		share/doc/%n
	<<
	DocFiles: ../README ../doc/copying.txt:LICENSE
<<
DescDetail: <<
NTL is a high-performance, portable c++ library providing data
structures and algorithms for manipulating signed, arbitrary length
integers, and for vectors, matrices, and polynomials over the integers
and over finite fields.
<<
DescPackaging: <<
	Configured to use the Gnu Multiple Precision library (gmp)

	Previously maintained by William McCallum.
<<
HomePage: https://www.shoup.net/ntl/
